<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Admin Setup Complete</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.1); padding: 2rem; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; text-align: center; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; color: #16a34a; }
    p  { color: #444; font-size: .875rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    a  { color: #1d4ed8; font-size: .875rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Admin account created</h1>
    <p>You can now log in and remove the <code>BOOTSTRAP_ADMIN_EMAIL</code> secret.</p>
    <a href="/admin">Go to admin dashboard</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
